  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2978307/" class="title-link">人生本无乡，何处是归程？</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2978307"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/Joanny/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u4477888-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Joanny/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Joanny</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-02-05"
      class="main-meta">2010-02-05 13:51:57</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2978307_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                        这是我第一次读宫部美雪的作品。    之前有意无意看过些对于她《火车》的评价，褒贬不一，有人非常推崇其厚重；也有人说推理过程无趣，比东野的《白夜行》差了十来条长安街，并因此愤愤不平，大呼“上当”。     而读过《理由》，我感觉，将宫部的作品简单定性为“推理小...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2978307/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">14有用 / 0没用</span>
